  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore, craft, build, and fight in this top down adventure RPG!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/347940/extras/a73c11a2a47f85f1f6e80b8f2d19a597.poster.avif?t=1759159631\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/347940/extras/a73c11a2a47f85f1f6e80b8f2d19a597.webm?t=1759159631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/347940/extras/a73c11a2a47f85f1f6e80b8f2d19a597.mp4?t=1759159631\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DISCOVER</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a procedurally generated world, mine resources, discover secrets, find treasures, and travel to distant lands!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/347940/extras/ef2b0c35cfb207bcf375fab5a3ac8575.poster.avif?t=1759159631\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/347940/extras/ef2b0c35cfb207bcf375fab5a3ac8575.webm?t=1759159631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/347940/extras/ef2b0c35cfb207bcf375fab5a3ac8575.mp4?t=1759159631\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BUILD</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your very own home! Gather resources and build in your own way. From wooden shacks, to obsidian brick fortresses. Plant charming gardens or herbs, construct animal pens, create extravagant vaults to display your rarest treasures. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/347940/extras/ca6fa32962baf53198693f9b2ddb263e.poster.avif?t=1759159631\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/347940/extras/ca6fa32962baf53198693f9b2ddb263e.webm?t=1759159631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/347940/extras/ca6fa32962baf53198693f9b2ddb263e.mp4?t=1759159631\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FIGHT</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle a variety of foes and formidable bosses and obtain new powerful equipment! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/347940/extras/ad439cb07df6fcbb765db5fa7d932701.poster.avif?t=1759159631\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/347940/extras/ad439cb07df6fcbb765db5fa7d932701.webm?t=1759159631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/347940/extras/ad439cb07df6fcbb765db5fa7d932701.mp4?t=1759159631\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Relax</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play at your own pace, and in your own style. Whether it's planting and growing crops, raising farm animals, fishing, crafting, collecting, or helping friendly NPCs you'll meet on your travels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/347940/extras/95f4449be5f4554b5a1d1716e21edd1e.avif?t=1759159631\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ITEMS</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 800+ items to find and collect! Obtained from a wide range of activities, including crafting, gathering, defeating monsters, treasure chests, fishing, and quest rewards!</p>",
